rows.label: qst002308_msg0001
rows.name:
Wh-whoa! Who're you?!
I wasn't slacking off, I swear!

rows.label: qst002308_msg0002
rows.name:
R-research? You're looking into
the security of Acedia?

rows.label: qst002308_msg0003
rows.name:
Oh, go on then. I'll tell you what you
want to know. Just don't mention me
in that article,okay?

rows.label: qst002308_msg0004
rows.name:
There are 23 guards here at night.
Is that all you were after?

rows.label: qst002308_msg0005
rows.name:
Now I'm gonna get back to my guard
station, so PLEASE don't tell anyone
you saw me here...
